lead_paragraph: A look at the U.S. team in the 41st Ryder Cup on Sept. 30-Oct. 2 at Hazeltine National in Chaska, Minnesota. Players are listed in the order they made the team.

headline.print_headline: RYDER CUP '16: Capsules of the American Players at Hazeltine
